Rune darts are Ranged throwing weapons that are only available to members. Rune darts require level 40 Ranged to wield. They can be obtained by either using the Smithing and Fletching skills or trading with another player. Rune darts can be poisoned and can be wielded with a shield or prayer book for protection.

To create rune darts the player must have completed the Tourist Trap quest and have at least level 89 Smithing and level 81 Fletching. Players can smith rune bars into rune dart tips. Each rune bar creates 10 rune dart tips and gives the player 75 Smithing experience. Feathers then must be added to create the rune darts. 18.8 Fletching experience is rewarded per rune dart.

Fletching a rune dart is also a potential Sherlock challenge step for a master clue.
